  "format": "A conversation that started as a Smashing Machine taping and turned into its own thing. Sean Fennessey and Amanda Dobbins sit with Van Lathan on 'One Battle After Another': the money PTA got to make it, who else gets that kind of shot, and Van's argument that the film's portrayal of Perfidia Beverly Hills fails Black women.",
  "segments": [
