      "films": [
        {
          "title": "One Battle After Another",
          "year": 2025,
          "note": "Van reveres the movie and still calls it 'some fuck shit': he doesn't get the gasps, ranks Lockjaw (Sean Penn) as the meatiest character, and argues the writing of Perfidia Beverly Hills (Teyana Taylor) as a selfish rat plays into tropes that fail Black women. Sean, four viewings in, reads her as a study in coercion and the film as a two-generation argument about revolution; Amanda keeps asking whether one tweak would have made it land."
